Flexible Single Master Operations (FSMO)
Check or Identify Current Server (PDC Emulator, RID Master, Domain Infrastructure Master, Naming Master, Schema Master)
Open Command line form any server and run this command.
  #netdom query fsmo

Change Role to another server
Open Command line from DC Server and run following commad.
  #ntdsutil
  #role
  #connections
  #connect to server SERVER_NAME     [target server which select for role]
  #quit         [quit from connection]
  #Transfer PDC               [Make connected server the PDC]
  #Transfer RID master       [Make connected server the RID master]
  #Transfer infrastructure master       [Make connected server the infrastructure master]
  #Transfer naming master             [Make connected server the naming master]
  #Transfer schema master             [Make connected server the schema master]
  #quit [for exit]

  
